    <h3 class="heading-medium" id="margins">Margins (Vertical spacing)</h3>

    <p class="text">Abstract classes that can handle vertical spacing will <abbr title="Don&rsquo;t Repeat Yourself">DRY</abbr> our code and allow for global consistency with spacing components.</p>

    <p>Margins are calculated in 5px increments.</p>

